      What's special

      Welcome to 116 Hunter Ave, a beautifully maintained home offering 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and 1005 sq ft of living space in the sought-after Oakland, CA area. Nestled on a spacious lot, this property boasts a generous backyard, providing ample room for outdoor enjoyment and potential expansion possibilities. This charming home, removed in 2022, is in excellent condition, presenting a fantastic opportunity for a short sale. Don't miss out on this chance to secure a wonderful property in great condition. Conveniently located, this home offers easy access to nearby amenities. Enjoy the convenience of being close to the airport, major freeways, and shopping malls, allowing for effortless travel and access to a variety of shopping, dining, and entertainment options.
